// src/components/About.jsx
import { Container, Typography, Grid, Box } from "@mui/material";
import { motion } from "framer-motion";

const fadeLeft = {
  hidden: { opacity: 0, x: -60 },
  visible: { opacity: 1, x: 0, transition: { duration: 0.9 } },
};

const fadeRight = {
  hidden: { opacity: 0, x: 60 },
  visible: { opacity: 1, x: 0, transition: { duration: 0.9 } },
};

const zoomIn = {
  hidden: { opacity: 0, scale: 0.85 },
  visible: { opacity: 1, scale: 1, transition: { duration: 0.8 } },
};

export default function About() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ py: 10, background: "linear-gradient(180deg,#f8fafc,#ffffff)" }}>
      <Container>

        {/* HEADER */}
        <motion.div initial="hidden" whileInView="visible" variants={zoomIn}>
          <Typography variant="h3" textAlign="center" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
            About PhysioTattva
          </Typography>

          <Typography
            variant="h6"
            textAlign="center"
            color="text.secondary"
            sx={{ maxWidth: 900, mx: "auto", mb: 8 }}
          >
            Healing through science, care and movement. We combine clinical expertise,
            modern technology and personalized therapy programs to restore mobility,
            strength and confidence.
          </Typography>
        </motion.div>

        {/* SECTION 1 */}
        <Grid container spacing={6} alignItems="center" sx={{ mb: 12 }}>
          {/* Text */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <motion.div initial="hidden" whileInView="visible" variants={fadeLeft}>
              <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
                Who We Are
              </Typography>

              <Typography sx={{ fontSize: "1.1rem", lineHeight: 1.8 }}>
                PhysioTattva is a leading physiotherapy and rehabilitation centre focused on
                restoring movement and improving quality of life. We provide evidence-based
                treatments supported by modern rehabilitation techniques and advanced equipment.
                Our mission is to deliver accurate diagnosis, compassionate care and long-term
                wellness solutions for every patient.
              </Typography>
            </motion.div>
          </Grid>

          {/* Image collage */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <motion.div initial="hidden" whileInView="visible" variants={fadeRight}>
              <Box sx={{ position: "relative", height: 420 }}>
                <motion.img
                  whileHover={{ scale: 1.05 }}
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550831107-1553da8c8464?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
                  style={{
                    width: "60%",
                    height: "300px",
                    objectFit: "cover",
                    borderRadius: "20px",
                    position: "absolute",
                    top: 0,
                    left: 0,
                    boxShadow: "0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)",
                  }}
                />

                <motion.img
                  whileHover={{ scale: 1.05 }}
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580281657521-6c5d3c1b9c92?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
                  style={{
                    width: "55%",
                    height: "280px",
                    objectFit: "cover",
                    borderRadius: "20px",
                    position: "absolute",
                    bottom: 0,
                    right: 0,
                    boxShadow: "0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)",
                  }}
                />
              </Box>
            </motion.div>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        {/* SECTION 2 */}
        <Grid container spacing={6} alignItems="center">
          {/* Image collage */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <motion.div initial="hidden" whileInView="visible" variants={fadeLeft}>
              <Box sx={{ position: "relative", height: 420 }}>
                <motion.img
                  whileHover={{ scale: 1.05 }}
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579154204601-01588f351e67?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
                  style={{
                    width: "60%",
                    height: "300px",
                    objectFit: "cover",
                    borderRadius: "20px",
                    position: "absolute",
                    top: 0,
                    right: 0,
                    boxShadow: "0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)",
                  }}
                />

                <motion.img
                  whileHover={{ scale: 1.05 }}
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606813902919-9f0c3a67c8fa?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
                  style={{
                    width: "55%",
                    height: "280px",
                    objectFit: "cover",
                    borderRadius: "20px",
                    position: "absolute",
                    bottom: 0,
                    left: 0,
                    boxShadow: "0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)",
                  }}
                />
              </Box>
            </motion.div>
          </Grid>

          {/* Text */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <motion.div initial="hidden" whileInView="visible" variants={fadeRight}>
              <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
                Our Clinics & Treatment
              </Typography>

              <Typography sx={{ fontSize: "1.1rem", lineHeight: 1.8 }}>
                PhysioTattva clinics are built with state-of-the-art infrastructure and modern
                rehabilitation equipment. Each patient receives a personalized treatment plan
                designed to ensure faster and safer recovery while improving strength, balance
                and mobility. Our holistic approach supports long-term wellbeing and independence.
              </Typography>
            </motion.div>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
}
